 <PERSON> Richard </PERSON> <PERSON> Pyle </PERSON>, an <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> correspondent based in <LOCATION> Bahrain </LOCATION>, covers the <LOCATION> Middle </LOCATION> <LOCATION> East </LOCATION>.
