<HEAD>Newspaper Case, Other Policy Decisions Face Embattled Meese</HEAD>
<NOTE>EDs: FIXES spelling of Ursula in 12th graf pvs bgng, `Meese this'</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By TIM BOVEE</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
